# SonicBridge Configuration

Copy this file to `.env.local` and update with your API keys:

## Last.fm Configuration (Optional)

To enable Last.fm scrobbling:

1. Get your API key: https://www.last.fm/api/account/create
2. Add your credentials:

```env
VITE_LASTFM_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
VITE_LASTFM_API_SECRET=your_api_secret_here
```

## Vercel Deployment Configuration (Optional)

If deploying to a non-Vercel backend, set the API URL:

```env
VITE_API_BASE=https://your-backend-url.com
```

Default: `/api` (relative URL for Vercel Functions)
